Subdirectories:
---------------

util       utility classes for scientific computation (namespace Util)
inter      classes defining potential energy functions (namespace Inter)
mcMd       serial Monte Carlo (MC) / molecular dynamics (MD) (namespace McMd)
ddMd       parallel domain-decomposition MD simulation (namespace DdMd)
modules    add-on components for particular applications
draft      unfinished or proposed classes

Files:
------

makefile      main makefile
compiler.mk_r compiler settings (repository version)
LICENSE       GPL license

The configure script also creates a file compiler.mk, which is created by
copying and modifying compiler.mk_r (the default version).

For compilation instructions, see the file src/dox/compile.dox, or the README 
file in the root directory (the parent of this directory).
